==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sauter
<hw>Sau`ter"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[F., properly,
to jump.]</ety> <def>To fry lightly and quickly, as meat, by turning or
tossing it over frequently in a hot pan greased with a little
fat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sauter</ent>⟦br⟧

